Atlantic City Electric Cosaid it will redeem all of its outstanding 5-7/8 pct cumulativeconvertible preferred stock.    The stock will be redeemed April 30 at the scheduledredemption price of 101.50 dlrs a share plus accrued and unpaiddividends.    The shares are also convertible until the redemption dateinto common stock at the rate of 3.5 common shares for eachpreferred share. The company has 10,855 of the 5-7/8 pctpreferred shares outstanding, it said. Reuter&#3;